sequenceDiagram
    actor Browser as Browser SPA
    participant Auth as Authorization Server

    Browser->>Browser: 1. verifier 生成・challenge 計算
    Browser->>Auth: 2. /authorize?code_challenge=...
    Auth->>Browser: 3. ログイン + 認可画面を表示
    Browser->>Auth: 4. 認可
    Auth->>Browser: 5. /redirect?code=XXX
    Browser->>Auth: 6. /token（code + verifier）
    Auth->>Browser: 7. access_token を返す
